    {
      "speaker": "Feanor",
      "text": "It’s still there, we can still save it.",
      "portraitName": "Feanor",
      "typingSpeed": 0.05
    },
    {
      "speaker": "Keiko",
      "text": "I can feel the resonance… It’s so faint…",
      "portraitName": "Keiko",
      "typingSpeed": 0.05
    },
    {
      "speaker": "Rona",
      "text": "Please let’s do everything we can, we can still save this.",
      "portraitName": "Rona",
      "typingSpeed": 0.05
    },
    {
      "speaker": "Murial",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "portraitName": "Murial",
      "typingSpeed": 0.05
    },
    {
      "speaker": "Rona",
      "text": "Kael?",
      "portraitName": "Rona",
      "typingSpeed": 0.05
    },
    {
      "speaker": "Kael",
      "text": "Alright.",
      "portraitName": "Kael",
      "typingSpeed": 0.05
    },
    {
      "speaker": "Kael",
      "text": "Ferry?",
      "portraitName": "Kael",
      "typingSpeed": 0.05
    },
    {
      "speaker": "Murial",
      "text": "We shouldn’t have trusted him!",
      "portraitName": "Murial",
      "typingSpeed": 0.05
    },
    {
      "speaker": "Keiko",
      "text": "That’s not the Ferry we know…",
      "portraitName": "Keiko",
      "typingSpeed": 0.05
    },
    {
      "speaker": "Ferry",
      "text": "Kael... you spent so many nights forcing yourself to keep going.",
      "portraitName": "Ferry",
      "typingSpeed": 0.05
    },
    {
      "speaker": "Ferry",
      "text": "And now look at what it became.",
      "portraitName": "Ferry",
      "typingSpeed": 0.05
    },
    {
      "speaker": "Ferry",
      "text": "Now, you have to pay the price.",
      "portraitName": "Ferry",
      "typingSpeed": 0.05
